These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 9

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-9-1::.
There are 4 different nationalities: indonesian, nigerian, american, australian
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: swimming, volleyball, soccer, surfing
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: country, d&b, rock, techno
 1. the indonesian is on the left or right of the australian##3
 2. the australian is on the left or right of the nigerian##3
 3. the fan rock is not to the right of the fan d&b##8
 4. the fan d&b is not to the left of the person who's sport is surfing##8
 5. the indonesian is in an even position##4
 6. the nigerian is on the right of the fan rock##1
 7. the person who's sport is swimming is the fan country##1
 8. the fan rock is not the person who's sport is surfing##6
 9. the fan d&b is somewhere to the right of the american##5
10. the american is not to the right of the person who's sport is soccer##8
11. the nigerian is not to the left of the american##8
12. the fan d&b is between the american and the person who's sport is volleyball##2
13. the fan rock and the person who's sport is soccer have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2        |     3     |    4    |
| Hobby         | american | nigerian      | australian | indonesian |
| Job           | soccer | surfing | volleyball      | swimming |
| Music-Genre   | rock        | d&b            | techno    | country |

