.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-9-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, iced-tea, milk, tea
4 different games are played: domino, backgammon, mah-jongg, poker
City: nizza, rome, liverpool, new-york
 1. the person playing mah-jongg is not to the right of the person traveling to nizza##8
 2. the person drinking iced-tea is not to the right of the person drinking milk##8
 3. the person traveling to rome and the person playing domino have the same parity positions##9
 4. the person playing mah-jongg is somewhere to the right of the person playing poker##5
 5. the person traveling to liverpool is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
 6. the person drinking 7up is not to the left of the person drinking iced-tea##8
 7. the person playing poker is not to the right of the person drinking tea##8
 8. the person traveling to rome is between the person drinking iced-tea and the person drinking milk##2
 9. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1
10. the person traveling to rome is on the left of the person playing poker##1
11. the person playing domino is not to the left of the person traveling to new-york##8
12. the person playing poker is not to the right of the person traveling to nizza##8
13. the person playing poker is on the left of the person playing mah-jongg##1
14. the person playing mah-jongg is not to the left of the person drinking tea##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2   |    3     |    4    |
| Beverage      | iced-tea | 7up   | milk     | tea     |
| Music-Genre   | backgammon    | domino   | poker      | mah-jongg    |
| Sport         | new-york   | rome | liverpool | nizza |

