.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-9-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: drawing, fishing, hiking, video-games
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, almond-milk, sprite, coffee
City: miami, colone, boston, venice
 1. the person who's hobby is drawing is not to the left of the person drinking milk##8
 2. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
 3. the person drinking sprite is the person who's hobby is drawing##1
 4. the person drinking sprite is somewhere between the person drinking coffee and the person traveling to colone##7
 5. the person who's hobby is video-games and the person drinking milk have different parity positions##9
 6. the person traveling to boston is not to the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##8
 7. the person traveling to boston is somewhere to the left of the person drinking coffee##5
 8. the person traveling to colone is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##5
 9. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
10. the person traveling to miami is between the person drinking milk and the person traveling to venice##2
11. the person who's hobby is fishing is not the person drinking milk##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |    4    |
| Hobby         | video-games | hiking     | drawing  | fishing |
| Nationality   | almond-milk       | milk    | sprite | coffee |
| Pet           | boston       | colone | miami     | venice  |

