.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-9-4::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, almond-milk, coffee, water
There 4 different types of food: artichoke, pumpkin, banana, pear
The people have 4 different jobs:  dancer, bartender, freelancer, police-officer
 1. the person drinking coffee and the person eating banana have the same parity positions##9
 2. the dancer and the person eating pumpkin have different parity positions##9
 3. the person eating artichoke is on the right of the person eating pumpkin##1
 4. the person eating pumpkin is somewhere to the left of the person drinking 7up##5
 5. the freelancer is on the left of the dancer##1
 6. the police-officer is on the left or right of the person drinking 7up##3
 7. the person drinking water is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
 8. the person eating artichoke is the dancer##1
 9. the person drinking coffee is somewhere to the left of the person eating pear##5
10. the person eating artichoke is between the freelancer and the person eating banana##2
11. the person drinking coffee is on the left or right of the bartender##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |     2      |    3    |      4      |
| Beverage   | water  | 7up        | coffee  | almond-milk |
| Hobby      | pumpkin  | artichoke    | banana | pear |
| Sport      | freelancer | dancer | police-officer | bartender    |

