4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, ferret, lizard, rabbit
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: pop, indie, disco, house
 1. the owner of the chinchilla is on the right of the fan pop##1
 2. the fan disco is on the right of the fan pop##1
 3. the fan indie is not the owner of the chinchilla##6
 4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person drinking water##1
 5. the person drinking hot-chocolate is somewhere to the left of the fan indie##5
 6. the person drinking water is somewhere to the left of the person drinking cola##5
 7. the person drinking cola and the fan indie have different parity positions##9
 8. the owner of the lizard is on the left or right of the owner of the ferret##3
 9. the owner of the ferret is on the left of the fan pop##1
10. the person drinking water is not to the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##8
11. the owner of the chinchilla is not the fan indie##6

